BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 524.00 Td (IMPORTANT: on the Python installer, tick 'Add python.exe to PATH'.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 54.00 494.00 Td (3. Get the code from GitHub) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 474.00 Td (git clone <YOUR-REPO-URL> jurisai) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 461.50 Td (cd jurisai) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 449.00 Td (Replace <YOUR-REPO-URL> with your repository URL. After cloning you will have two) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 435.00 Td (folders: backend/ and frontend/.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 54.00 405.00 Td (4. Backend setup \(Django API\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 385.00 Td (Open a terminal in the project folder and run these one block at a time:) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 371.00 Td (cd backend) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 358.50 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 346.00 Td (# create and activate a virtual environment) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 333.50 Td (python -m venv venv) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 321.00 Td (venv\\Scripts\\activate # Windows \(PowerShell / CMD\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 308.50 Td (# source venv/bin/activate # macOS / Linux) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 296.00 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 283.50 Td (# install all Python dependencies) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 271.00 Td (pip install -r requirements.txt) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 258.50 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 246.00 Td (# create the database tables \(SQLite, no setup needed\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 233.50 Td (python manage.py makemigrations) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 221.00 Td (python manage.py migrate) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 208.50 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 196.00 Td (# \(optional\) create an admin login for /admin + Admin console) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 183.50 Td (python manage.py createsuperuser) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 171.00 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 158.50 Td (# start the API server) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 146.00 Td (python manage.py runserver) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 133.50 Td (Leave this terminal running. The API is now at http://localhost:8000 .) Tj ET
