BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 798.00 Td (for security, so create it from the template after cloning:) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 784.00 Td (# inside the backend/ folder) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 771.50 Td (copy .env.example .env # Windows) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 759.00 Td (# cp .env.example .env # macOS / Linux) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 746.50 Td (Then open backend/.env and set your free Google Gemini key:) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 732.50 Td (LLM_PROVIDER=auto) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 720.00 Td (GEMINI_API_KEY=<paste-your-gemini-key-here>) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 707.50 Td (GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 695.00 Td (Get a free key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey \(a valid key usually starts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 681.00 Td (with 'AIza'\). Restart the server after editing .env. WITHOUT a key the app still) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 667.00 Td (works using built-in offline answers and summaries.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 54.00 637.00 Td (6. Frontend setup \(React\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 617.00 Td (Open a SECOND terminal \(keep the backend running in the first one\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 603.00 Td (cd frontend) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 590.50 Td (npm install) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 66.00 578.00 Td (npm run dev) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 565.50 Td (This starts the app at http://localhost:5173 and usually opens it automatically.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 551.50 Td (If the backend is not running, the frontend shows sample 'demo' data so every) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 537.50 Td (screen still works.) Tj ET
