BT /F1 10 Tf 64.00 389.50 Td (  language, download as PDF.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 64.00 375.50 Td (- Clause Verification: upload a contract to see a risk score, flagged loopholes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 64.00 361.50 Td (  and corrected wording.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 54.00 331.50 Td (8. Troubleshooting) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 64.00 311.50 Td (- 'python' is not recognized: reinstall Python with 'Add to PATH' ticked, or use) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 64.00 297.50 Td (  'py' instead of 'python'.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 64.00 283.50 Td (- pip fails building PyMuPDF: upgrade pip first -> python -m pip install) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 64.00 269.50 Td (  --upgrade pip) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 64.00 255.50 Td (- Port already in use: run the API on another port -> python manage.py runserver) Tj ET
